AUDIO: 'So first of all, you can see it show you the list of parts, you can explode them and review and we can start adding connectors. I\'m going to press add all connectors and we can review them. There are three types of connector supported ball'

[06:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'joints, pin and dovetail. Most of the time I use dovetail and not only you can set the shape but you can control scale, assembly fit, connection depths and angle. You can control them'

[06:19] [scene:talk]
