AUDIO: 'Here we go with the results. We can assemble it. Also, there is another preview mode, which is x-ray and we can actually see how tight the connectors go. You can control assembly fit parameter. If you choose loose,'

[07:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'the hole will be basically bigger than the connector and the opposite. The tight will make it like one to one. I personally advise to keep some space because after printing, there might be some painting job, etc.'

