AUDIO: 'Because technically, yes, you can, but since this still is generative AI, there might be some imperfection that you want to address. And for this, I really recommend Blender since there\'s a free tool and there is a sculpting mode, which is'

[08:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'absolutely insane, super easy and fun. And you can address any issue. Let me show you. So we\'re going to bring it to Blender. And by the way, we\'re going to need to create connectors for the legs. We\'re going to review that all the connectors'

