[09:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'And by the way, before we continue, guys, if you\'re new to Blender, I have videos specifically for you. It\'s made for complete beginners. And just after one evening, you\'ll be quite good with Blender. Link is here.'

[09:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'So as I said, smooth brush is what I use 50% of time. And also you can access it when you work in any other brush by holding shift. All buttons that I press, you can see here on the screen.'

[09:59] [scene:talk]
